		<div class="comment-body"><p>Hi. I&#8217;ve made these before following the exact recipe and had good results. However, I&#8217;m wondering what improvements I could make. Looking through some of the comments, do you recommend now using only bread flour or a mix of bread and all-purpose? Also, do you recommend refrigerating the dough before baking?</p>
<p>One final question&#8211;do you think I could half the entire recipe and it would turn out ok?</p>
</div>

		<div class="reply">
			<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2007/10/18/jaays-best-ever-chocolate-chip-cookies/?replytocom=872#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-872", "872", "respond", "233")'>Reply</a>		</div><!-- .reply -->
