		<div class="comment-body"><p>Gideon,</p>
<p>If you want the cookies to be thicker, try bread flour.  I&#8217;ve found I like half all purpose, half bread flour.  But it&#8217;s personal taste.  I still haven&#8217;t tried refrigerating, but it&#8217;s worth a test.  I&#8217;ve heard both that it helps and that it makes no difference.</p>
<p>You could probably cut it in half, but I&#8217;d figure out the weights, then do half the recipe by weight.</p>
</div>

